# Relationships
Member      1--1 User
Member      1--1 Admin
User        *--* User {label: "friends"}
User        1--* Post
User        1--* Comment
Message_Thread      1--* Message_Thread_Users
Message_Thread      1--* Message
Message_Thread_Users        1--* User
